ariba.ui.wizard.meta
Class WizardFrameMeta

java.lang.Object
  ariba.ui.wizard.meta.GenericMeta
      ariba.ui.wizard.meta.WizardFrameMeta

public final class WizardFrameMeta
extends GenericMeta

A WizardFrameMeta is the runtime counterpart to an XML definition of a wizard frame. It represents the static information about a frame in a wizard flow, i.e. name, label, content source, delegate class, etc.
